\ab\ai\af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs18\b\i\f1\fs32\cf6\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid8548906 Song 2.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906  
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs18\i\f1\cf6\insrsid8548906 Eirmos:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs36 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs21\f1\fs36\cf15\cgrid0\insrsid8548906 
Attend, O heaven, and I will speak, and will sing of Christ who came to dwell among us in flesh which He took from the Virgin. 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs18\i\f1\cf6\insrsid8548906 Refrain:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs36 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs21\f1\fs36\cf15\cgrid0\insrsid8548906 
Have mercy on me, O God, have mercy on me.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906  
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs18\i\f1\cf6\insrsid8548906 Troparia:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906  
\par 
\par Sin which stripped me of my former God-woven clothing has also sewn on me coats of skin. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs16\insrsid8548906 (Genesis 3:21)}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906  
\par 
\par I am wrapped in a garment of shame as with fig leaves, in reproof of my selfish passions. 
\par 
\par I am clad in a coat that is spotted and shamefully blood-stained by the flow of my passionate and pleasure-loving life. 
\par 
\par I fell under the burden of passions and corruption of matter, and from then until now I am oppressed by the enemy. 
\par 
\par Having preferred a possessive and pleasure-loving life to spiritual poverty, O Savior, I am now harnessed with a heavy yoke. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs16\insrsid8548906 (Matthew 5:3) 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906 
\par I have adorned the idol of my flesh with the many-colored clothing of shameful thoughts, and I am condemned. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs16\insrsid8548906 (1 John 5:21) 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906 
\par I have been anxiously concerned only about outward adornment, and have neglected the inner temple made in the image of God. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs16\insrsid8548906 (I Peter 3:3-4)}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906  
\par 
\par I have buried with passions the beauty of the original image, O Savior. But seek and find it, like the lost coin. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs16\insrsid8548906 (Luke 15:8) 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906 
\par Like the harlot I cry to Thee: I have sinned, I alone have sinned against Thee. Accept my tears also, O Savior, as perfume. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs16\insrsid8548906 (Luke 7:37-50)}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906  
\par 
\par Like the publican I cry to Thee: Be merciful, O Savior, be merciful to me; for no child of Adam has sinned as I against Thee. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs16\insrsid8548906 (Luke 18:13)}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906  
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs36 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs21\f1\fs36\cf15\cgrid0\insrsid8548906 Glory to the Father, and to the Son, and to the Holy Spirit: 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs18\i\f1\cf6\insrsid8548906 To The Trinity:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906  One in three Persons I praise Thee, O God of all, the Father, the Son, and the Holy Spirit. 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs36 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs21\f1\fs36\cf15\cgrid0\insrsid8548906 Now and ever, and to the ages of ages. Amen. 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs18\i\f1\cf6\insrsid8548906 Theotokion:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906  Spotless Mother of God, only all-hymned Virgin, pray intensely that we may be saved. 
\par 
