\par 
\par In Thee the Conqueror of death, I have found the Source of Life, and from my heart I cry to Thee before my end: I have sinned, be merciful, save me. 
\par 
\par I have sinned, O Lord, I have sinned against Thee. Be merciful to me. For there is no one who has sinned among men whom I have not surpassed by my sins. 
\par 
\par I have imitated those who were licentious in Noah's time, and I have earned a share in their condemnation of drowning in the flood. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs16\insrsid8548906 (Genesis 6) 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906 
\par You have imitated Ham, that spurner of his father, my soul. You have not concealed your neighbor\rquote s shame by returning to him looking backwards. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs16\insrsid8548906 (Genesis 9:20 27}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906 ) 
\par 
