 I am the Trinity, simple and undivided, divided Personally, and I am the Unity, united in nature, says the Father, the Son, and the Divine Spirit. 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs36 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs21\f1\fs36\cf15\cgrid0\insrsid8548906 Now and ever, and to the ages of ages. Amen. 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ai\af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs18\i\f1\cf6\insrsid8548906 Theotokion:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\f1\fs32\insrsid8548906  Thy womb bore God for
 us Who took our form. Implore Him as the Creator of all, O Mother of God that through thy intercessions we may be justified. 
\par 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qc \li0\ri0\keep\widctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\ai\af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs18\b\i\f1\fs32\cf6\lang1024\langfe1024\noproof\insrsid8548906 Kontakion, tone 6:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 
