\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs36 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs21\f1\fs36\cf15\cgrid0\insrsid8548906 My soul, my soul, arise! Why are you sleeping? The end is drawing near, and you will be confounded. Awake, 
